{"tid":336280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6歲男童大圍名城泳池遇溺　一度昏迷","createTime":"2017-07-26T10:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T10:59:23.000Z","uid":118114,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"293a4d5067135f879d771ae4bcb39e75b04166ba","tid":336280,"uid":118114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/26/175836_42032e1213f980a10b5a222f268e98a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F26%2F175836_42032e1213f980a10b5a222f268e98a3.jpg&h=df69cf37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下午3時許，大圍美田路一個私人屋苑會所泳池內，一名姓鍾（6歲）男童學習游泳期間遇溺，家人見狀即時將他救起，然後通知保安員報警求助。救護員接報到場，男童已陷於昏迷，由救護車送院，經搶救已經甦醒，現時仍在醫院接受治理，一名男親友趕至了解。警方接報到場經初步調查，相信事件起因無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n唔識教水就咪害人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 教得小朋友水既都知安全第一架啦 泳池溺親真係世界級 <br />\n利申 我教小朋友游水既目標係唔好浸親佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d8dd2ae95f4f15b32daf1c57dcbca81b1e5572","tid":336280,"uid":94774,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:22:07.000Z","msg":"以前見D教練係扔細路仔落水<br />\n扔到唔驚為止"},{"pid":"c27973507781cf583f4feaa02f2c1d9ad5f21ed0","tid":336280,"uid":52591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:29:14.000Z","msg":"個教練無啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89032b1e677ceb0bd8f81b7ba6c88e5a3f14f1e2","tid":336280,"uid":6604,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:46:22.000Z","msg":"名城多蝗"},{"pid":"d725debf00fe70016be584e52551911678ab84b7","tid":336280,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:48:53.000Z","msg":"咁識投胎<br />\n死左未?"},{"pid":"15ca5de673fcae81c13700d6596e1dd5ff8d4321","tid":336280,"uid":49815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:50:46.000Z","msg":"點會無可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見過教水1:10 點睇得曬"},{"pid":"713fd06871a5310904353af503d6a4c28fd27ff4","tid":336280,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T11:00:17.000Z","msg":"1米3-4深都浸親就一定教練問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4addc6b60efba5420b5d2d04473e29957d987e03","tid":336280,"uid":118114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T11:13:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點會無可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見過教水1:10 點睇得曬</blockquote><br />\n通常咁大班都係sure安全先比一次過落水<br />\n例如有書包仔或者水袖"},{"pid":"29bf0f3c41b98bb6783e8cb903a882aced33bace","tid":336280,"uid":34858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T11:31:46.000Z","msg":"下 冇人睇住佢架咩"},{"pid":"d096ba3e5b0f3b9fc351cfb7c1edb7361f2de0e9","tid":336280,"uid":72902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T11:41:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前見D教練係扔細路仔落水<br />\n扔到唔驚為止</blockquote><br />\n我係其畫個比人扔<br />\n扔完真係唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfca3077c26a8cccf765f38f33a29b7f178e8939","tid":336280,"uid":90585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T11:43:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前見D教練係扔細路仔落水<br />\n扔到唔驚為止</blockquote><br />\n我就係咁 之後一直學唔識  亦無再學<br />\n直到大大下 到一定年齡 先自學識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad62e1956cee8b4271c9f2fce2aa25e0851330e","tid":336280,"uid":110282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T12:27:35.000Z","msg":"救生員做緊咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bfad44fb76c519dea324c00a1642eb83eb689df","tid":336280,"uid":20074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T12:30:42.000Z","msg":"邊度寫有教練？<br />\n學習游泳一定要教練教?"},{"pid":"ca2a53e0d8c564ac3978a99d4d3226f534b92213","tid":336280,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T14:34:58.000Z","msg":"屋苑泳池深得去邊 都出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"578abe40a79a17ddd799a028e05ceffd616d3598","tid":336280,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T14:39:49.000Z","msg":"令我諗起小學個陣有個同學浸死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地約堆去游泳池,之後玩斗潛水唔抖氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最尾幾個都唔夠氣,就踩住果個同學上岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f855d22fe75b81226ef74ab9459ed9da3efaa54e","tid":336280,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T14:41:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊度寫有教練？<br />\n學習游泳一定要教練教?</blockquote><br />\n咪係，家人即刻將佢救起，咁即係家人帶佢去學游水啦"},{"pid":"73ff52096d59e7bbc3a71b1a2b1a668537ed9a90","tid":336280,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T14:46:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>令我諗起小學個陣有個同學浸死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地約堆去游泳池,之後玩斗潛水唔抖氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最尾幾個都唔夠氣,就踩住果個同學上岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學下組織同打字先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73c112dc49c4083c5ae5bf09ee22ff072416666a","tid":336280,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T14:54:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7月搵替身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n2017/04/10<br />\n<br />\n仵工將死者屍體舁送殮房<br />\n<br />\n早上7時許，沙田大圍美田路1號「名城」有一名男子從高處墮下，跌正屋苑的泳池內，被保安發現時已昏迷，救護員接報到場，證實死亡，毋須送院。警員事後調查，證實死者姓陳(42歲)，警方及後檢獲一封遺書，透露因病及金錢問題不開心尋死，警方認為無可疑，列作有人從高處墮下死亡。事後由仵工將其屍體舁送殮房，稍後由法醫剖屍確定死因。"},{"pid":"b8adaf99c6636fa33e0f58b011fa84a254ac0435","tid":336280,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T15:58:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7月搵替身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n2017/04/10<br />\n<br />\n仵工將死者屍體舁送殮房<br />\n<br />\n早上7時許，沙田大圍美田路1號「名城」有一名男子從高處墮下，跌正屋苑的泳池內，被保安發現時已昏迷，救護員接報到場，證實死亡，毋須送院。警員事後調查，證實死者姓陳(42歲)，警方及後檢獲一封遺書，透露因病及金錢問題不開心尋死，警方認為無可疑，列作有人從高處墮下死亡。事後由仵工將其屍體舁送殮房，稍後由法醫剖屍確定死因。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b590ee285daf69dc3ce4100b26acadad94321cd4","tid":336280,"uid":59705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T08:13:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7月搵替身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n2017/04/10<br />\n<br />\n仵工將死者屍體舁送殮房<br />\n<br />\n早上7時許，沙田大圍美田路1號「名城」有一名男子從高處墮下，跌正屋苑的泳池內，被保安發現時已昏迷，救護員接報到場，證實死亡，毋須送院。警員事後調查，證實死者姓陳(42歲)，警方及後檢獲一封遺書，透露因病及金錢問題不開心尋死，警方認為無可疑，列作有人從高處墮下死亡。事後由仵工將其屍體舁送殮房，稍後由法醫剖屍確定死因。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874884525f45934dc4bff1be0c37b8d75babe82e","tid":336280,"uid":69886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T08:15:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>令我諗起小學個陣有個同學浸死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地約堆去游泳池,之後玩斗潛水唔抖氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最尾幾個都唔夠氣,就踩住果個同學上岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廢柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0392bc8b1ab4d3c21a10fa0bda54bf5f17442af7","tid":336280,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:59:23.000Z","msg":"名城好似有好多支那蝗住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}